{"builtWith":"0.15.15","comments":[{"LineComment":" ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━"},{"LineComment":"                                   // hydrogen // element // transform-editor"},{"LineComment":" ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━"},{"LineComment":" | TransformEditor — Property panel for 2D and 3D transforms."},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | Provides unified UI for editing transforms with clear visual differentiation"},{"LineComment":" | between 2D operations (X, Y, rotation) and 3D operations (Z axis, perspective,"},{"LineComment":" | gimbal controls)."},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Design Philosophy"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | At billion-agent scale, transform editing must be:"},{"LineComment":" | - **Type-safe**: 2D and 3D are distinct types with distinct UI"},{"LineComment":" | - **Bounded**: All values clamped to valid ranges"},{"LineComment":" | - **Visual**: 3D includes gimbal preview, 2D shows transform origin"},{"LineComment":" | - **Composable**: Each section can be used independently"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Usage"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ```purescript"},{"LineComment":" | import Hydrogen.Element.Compound.TransformEditor as TE"},{"LineComment":" | "},{"LineComment":" | -- 2D transform editor"},{"LineComment":" | TE.transform2DEditor"},{"LineComment":" |   [ TE.transform2D state.transform"},{"LineComment":" |   , TE.onTransform2DChange UpdateTransform"},{"LineComment":" |   ]"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | -- 3D transform editor with gimbal"},{"LineComment":" | TE.transform3DEditor"},{"LineComment":" |   [ TE.transform3D state.transform3D"},{"LineComment":" |   , TE.onTransform3DChange UpdateTransform3D"},{"LineComment":" |   , TE.showGimbal true"},{"LineComment":" |   ]"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | -- Standalone sections"},{"LineComment":" | TE.translateSection2D state.translate ChangeTranslate"},{"LineComment":" | TE.rotateSection3D state.rotate ChangeRotate  -- shows gimbal"},{"LineComment":" | ```"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Module Structure"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | This is a leader module that re-exports from submodules:"},{"LineComment":" | - `TransformEditor.Props` — Types, defaults, and prop builders"},{"LineComment":" | - `TransformEditor.Editors` — Complete 2D and 3D editor components"},{"LineComment":" | - `TransformEditor.Sections` — Individual section components"},{"LineComment":" | - `TransformEditor.Internal` — Helper elements (not re-exported)"}],"decls":[],"exports":[],"foreign":[],"imports":[{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[84,15],"start":[81,1]}},"moduleName":["Hydrogen","Element","Compound","TransformEditor","Editors"]},{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[79,13],"start":[64,1]}},"moduleName":["Hydrogen","Element","Compound","TransformEditor","Props"]},{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[96,16],"start":[86,1]}},"moduleName":["Hydrogen","Element","Compound","TransformEditor","Sections"]},{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[96,16],"start":[49,1]}},"moduleName":["Prim"]}],"moduleName":["Hydrogen","Element","Compound","TransformEditor"],"modulePath":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Compound/TransformEditor.purs","reExports":{"Hydrogen.Element.Compound.TransformEditor.Editors":["transform2DEditor","transform3DEditor"],"Hydrogen.Element.Compound.TransformEditor.Props":["className","compactMode","defaultProps2D","defaultProps3D","onTransform2DChange","onTransform3DChange","showGimbal","showOriginPreview","transform2D","transform3D"],"Hydrogen.Element.Compound.TransformEditor.Sections":["originSection","perspectiveSection","rotateSection2D","rotateSection3D","scaleSection2D","scaleSection3D","skewSection2D","translateSection2D","translateSection3D"]},"sourceSpan":{"end":[96,16],"start":[49,1]}}